Wind Energy Is A Long-Term Investment.
We Help You To Protect It.





Dialight A/S is the market leader in supplying aviation obstructions lights
and marine aids to navigation solutions for the wind industry.


 









We develop & deliver state-of-the-art solutions that prevent collision with air traffic and maritime navigation enabling your wind project to comply with international and national regulation. 


 










We Work With the Best Companies In the World





Our customers for our aviation obstruction and aids to navigation products are virtually all wind turbine manufacturers such as Alstom, Areva, GE, Gamesa, Nordex, Senvion, Siemens and Vestas, the major foundation manufacturers such as Bladt Industries, EEW and Smulders, energy utilities such as Dong Energy and RES and wind service companies working in the field of retrofitting such as Deutsche Windtechnik.
 
See our References












Our aviation obstruction and aids to navigation components have been installed in more than 40 offshore wind projects.


 








 






