Our Products






  



											Aviation					 

Since the 1990’s, we have supplied aviation obstruction lights to the wind industry, constantly improving and expanding our product portfolio.






  



											Navigation					 

Our first offshore project to be supplied with Dialight’s solution dates back to 2000. Our marine aids to navigation components are today installed in all major offshore markets.


 
