UK Site



LED Lighting for Hazardous AreasDialight's SafeSite® LED lighting is designed to replace conventional lighting in a wide variety of hazardous area applications both indoor and outdoor where explosion protection is required. These include oil, gas & petrochemical, power generation, mining, chemical, pharmaceutical, water & sewage, food & beverage facilities and more.
 Typical applications are:• Hard to access areas where Ex e inspections are expensive• Locations requiring continuous and consistent light levels in extreme ambient temperatures• Areas requiring frequent switching on and off of lights• Where flammable vapours, gases, ignitable dusts, fibres or flyings are present, indoors or outdoors• Where extremely corrosive , wet, dusty, hot and/or cold conditions exist • Marine, wet locations and hose-down environments, areas subject to shock and vibration
 LED Lighting for Industrial AreasDialight's DuroSite® LED lighting is designed for heavy and general industrial applications to replace conventional lighting both indoor and outdoor. These include manufacturing, warehousing, cold storage, data centres and more.
Typical applications are:• High ceilinged areas where lighting maintenance is disruptive• Areas wishing to reduce their energy use and CO2 emissions• Areas of intermittent traffic that would benefit from switching on-and-off of lights or by dimming lights • Areas subject to shock and high vibration• Where wet, dusty, hot and/or cold conditions exist• Where quality of light is essential 
 


 













                 
            



























                 
            





