  Michael Sutsko, Group Chief Executive, said: 

  "We are focused on executing the Group's ambitious growth strategy as we seek to capture the opportunity in the industrial LED lighting market. The transformation to a robust and scalable manufacturing platform has advanced significantly in the period. We have completed platform engineering, and nine out of twelve product lines have transferred to our manufacturing partner with the final three lines to be completed by the end of the year. We remain excited by the Group's prospects and remain confident of delivering continued growth and shareholder value. Our expectations for the second half of 2017 remain unchanged." 

  Results presentation: 

  A presentation to analysts and investors will be held today at 09.00 GMT at Investec Bank Plc's offices at, 2 Gresham Street, London EC2V 7QP, United Kingdom. The presentation and an audiocast will be made available on the company's website, www.dialight.com. 

  Contacts: 

  Dialight Plc 

  Michael Sutsko - Group Chief Executive 

  Tel: +44 (0)203 058 3542 

  Fariyal Khanbabi - Group Finance Director 

  Tel: +44 (0)203 058 3542 

  MHP Communications 

  Tim Rowntree 

